Check out my piece in the @BurlcoTimes on the #GOPTaxScam that screws #NJ families: http://bit.ly/2Al0qsx 

Before the Senate passes their bill, I want to make sure you know this is welfare for the wealthy, paid for by the rest of us... simple as that.

"The tax legislation will devastate Medicaid to pay for the cuts, as well as penalize those of us who pay high local taxes because we live in a state & county that provides the services needed. This is a travesty." -Barbara, Collingswood, NJ
 
#GOPTaxScam

"I'm $200K in debt from student loans over the course of my academic career...If the Republican bill passes, my taxes would rise from less than $1000 to over $5000, leaving me with take-home pay that isn't enough to survive on."-Kevin, doctoral student, Westmont, NJ
 
#GOPTaxScam

"I live on a fixed income. With this tax plan, I will see my taxes go from appox. $1,000 to $7,000 a year. In addition, I’ll lose my medical expense & property tax deductions. I wouldn't be able to survive." -Mary from Collingswood, NJ

#GOPTaxScam

"Many aspects of the tax bill will have a severely negative impact for me & my family & I need you to fight to include the unreimbursed employee expenses deduction (even if with limitations)." -Steven from Sicklerville, #NJ
#GOPTaxScam

#GOPTaxScam
